title: Frank Lloyd Wright Designs Magnetic Bookmark Set
description:
This set of Frank Lloyd Wright Designs Magnetic Bookmarks borrows design patterns from the famed architect to create an exceptional reading accessory. The six die-cut magnetic clips feature unique patterns that will add flair to any book or magazine page.
  • Package Dimensions: 2.88 x 0.13 x 8.88 in.
  • Magnet Dimensions: 1 x 2 in.
  • Materials: 6 Magnetic bookmark clips
